# Asset Management Engine

## Purpose

Maintain an accurate inventory of managed assets and provide operational awareness of endpoint health, lifecycle status, and patch compliance.

---

## Inputs

- Active Directory
- Endpoint Inventory
- PowerShell Discovery
- Backup Status
- Patch Status

---

## Processing

- Inventory reconciliation.
- Lifecycle tracking.
- Patch verification.
- Backup validation.
- Operating system classification.

---

## Outputs

- Asset Inventory
- Lifecycle Report
- Patch Compliance Report
- Backup Status Report

---

## Metrics

|Metric|Description|
|---|---|
|Total Assets|Managed endpoints|
|Patch Compliance|Percentage fully patched|
|Unsupported Systems|End-of-support assets|
|Backup Success|Successful backup percentage|
|Offline Assets|Assets not reporting|

